values: I have a lot of them. they need to all go away now!

well i had to face the reality that my actions can lead to something life changing. i had to face the music and take a dreaded test that could have turned my whole life around. things turned out to be negative but never the less life lesson learned. the thoughts that have been occupying my mind the past 2 weeks has made me think and rethink alot of what i thought and believe.
something is not working right with me. i am not sure if i should do it or not. i hate this. mother nature is not being kind to me right now. shit!

I can't wait to get on the road again.

I will be in NC tonight and tomorrow
next week I will be in Orlando, Winter Haven, West Palm Beach and Miami<-----HELP ME!!!!!!! i hate hate hate Miami.


*scream!!!!!!!!!!!!!*

between my friend and his girlfriend. the girlfriend of my friend came up to me last night and pulled me aside to talk to me about the problems she is having with her boyfriend. i played stupid like i didn't know that there were any problems. i of course know because my friend has told me he is not wanting anything serious but his girlfriend is starting to demand something serious. so anyway, his girlfriend is telling me last night she thinks he is being lame for not facing a relationship with maturity, i have to agree w/ her but i did not say anything, i just listened. anyhow her boyfriend walks up to us and she turned to him and told him to "Fuck Off". so he was obviously pissed off and walked off. she was playing when she said that but he did not take it as such, so they had to run off and have a massive talk. fast forward to the party. we are all outside talking and of course the subject of sex comes up. my girlfriends and i are talking about the difficulties of having sex with a guy who is well, not large. haha sorry. anyway so she pipes in with her comments and it apparently pissed her boyfriend off. so another talk had to happend.  fast forward yet again to the apt. we are all there and i walk to the kitchen and i ask my friend if the strips to test how drunk you are really work, so he said tired it. i then yell out "oh this is like a pregnancy test, not that i have ever taken one!" well chime in my friends girlfriend. she drops the bomb on her boyfriend and said "oh yeah well i took one about 2 mths ago, because i was 2 weeks late!" she then died laughing. i looked over at my friend and saw the blood from his face drain. it ruined his night because she never told him about this until then. so she went to bed and then i am hanging out with my male friends. i tell my friend that I love him and he yells out at me "Iris you have been nothing but trouble for me tonight!" and walks out pissed off. i jumped from my seat and ran out after him to talk. i told him i did not start this shit all of it was brought about because i happend to be there and it forced some confessions. he was ok but man he was not happy. so he said, "alright you, *myboytoy* and I are going out right now!" so off we went. i spent the whole night and my morning with them. drinking, playing pool and talking.
went out to a club and stayed out until 6:45AM then went to the Waffle House with my boy toy and my friend. BUT nothing happend with my boy toy. i was a good girl. i only received a kiss. ;)

i went out last night and did not come home until 4:30AM. my friend and I walked about 2 miles back to the apt from the bar because our friends would not give up their Golden Tee game. haha. boy am i learning more and more about the male gender. interesting folk and ideals y'all have. ;)

my friends sent out pics yesterday afternoon to an email list that consisted of about 30 addresses and w/ people i have never met. included in one email was a set of pics of me. people who i never met before were coming up to me patting me on the back and shaking my hand! hahaha! all because i was holding a bottle of Hennesey in one pic followed by a pic of me past out on a chair with the wall holding me up. and another pic of me at the bar in a pimp hat,holding a cigar and sipping a pint of guinness. ;)  fun times. 

tonight is a warehouse party $10.00 will get you in to have all the beer and food you want. there will be 4 bands performing. i am not sure how long we are going to last because my friend and i have to be up by 7:30 AM tomorrow morning so that we can make it to a English pub to watch the live Man United vs. Liverpool match. it is going to be rough.

i am tired. i just watched Bend It Like Beckham. what a cute and entertaining movie. the coach was pretty hot. ;)
i am not a computer geek, i am not sure if I am using this properly.

for those curious souls who are interested in my day to day life as Samantha Jones, you will now have a place to read about my sexcapades,adventures of Travel and the drama I have with my job, boy toys, boys I cannot have, etc.

anyhow welcome and enjoy and post your damn comments! :)
